name: Hoshino Miyako | Watashi ni tenshi ga maiorita!
description:
Who?

  • Old lora I made when lora was released, and an a v2.0 improved version that I made recently.

  • This lora requires to use many tags to work properly, but offers more flexibility.

Tags:

(just copy and paste as far as you need, ordered from head to bottom)

  • "anime coloring" for flat colors

  • "anime screencap" for anime style

V2.0:

main costume:

hoshino_miyako, red hair, red eyes, short hair, hair over one eye

, track jacket, white shirt, t-shirt, collarbone

, track pants

, socks, no shoes

"partially unzipped" or "open jacket"

V1.0:

only use "hoshino_miyako"

, track jacket, white shirt

, track pants
